label: MedicalEvidenceLevel
comment: Level of evidence for a medical guideline. Enumerated type.

enumerationMembers.label: EvidenceLevelA
enumerationMembers.comment: Data derived from multiple randomized clinical trials or meta-analyses.

enumerationMembers.label: EvidenceLevelB
enumerationMembers.comment: Data derived from a single randomized trial, or nonrandomized studies.

enumerationMembers.label: EvidenceLevelC
enumerationMembers.comment: Only consensus opinion of experts, case studies, or standard-of-care.
